description.en: Republic of Dogs (ROD) is a Proprietary, Hyper Deflationary token on the Binance smart chain network. We aim to make a positive impact by collaborating with community chosen charitable projects. Our holders are rewarded with ROD tokens without having to lift a paw! On top of the automated buybacks from the Saviour Wallet with every market sell, "calltheSAVIOUR" will be activated at certain milestones. Scroll down for more information.
